      <title>纽约市遭遇超乎预期的快速移动暴风雪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/nyc-walloped-by-snow-storm-that-far-exceeds-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长假周末伊始，一场令人惊讶的猛烈冬季风暴席卷了纽约市，大雪覆盖了纽约市，导致街道湿滑并覆盖着粉末，并在一周内第二次延误了航空旅行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/nyc-walloped-by-snow-storm-that-far-exceeds-forecasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
